Package: missingtool
Title: Count Missing Values by Group
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Juntai", "Cao", , "juntai.cao@ubc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a simple wrapper to count missing values (NAs) across
    all columns for each level of a grouping variable. Useful for quickly 
    assessing data quality and missing patterns in grouped data.
